channel.title: Problem Setting Up My 508HD
channel.description:
Hey Moparscapers, Ive recent started setting up a 508HD server, but I have encountered a problem that probably all of you have seen before. Connecting To Update Server... The problem is not because I ran the client before the source, I ran the source before the client. Also I followed the "[508]: High Definition setup Pics+Explained" TUT. I correctly INSTALLED the titan cache and put in the regular cache508 in it. Please help ASAP. Thanks In Advance,
~Zofis
